graph LR
    TrustyAI[TrustyAI Service Operator]

    %% External Platform Dependencies
    TrustyAI -->|container orchestration| K8s[Kubernetes v1.19+]
    TrustyAI -->|routes & OAuth| OpenShift[OpenShift v4.6+<br/>Optional]
    TrustyAI -->|metrics scraping| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator v0.64.1<br/>Optional]
    TrustyAI -->|TLS certificates| CertMgr[cert-manager /<br/>OpenShift Cert Service]

    %% External Storage Dependencies
    TrustyAI -.->|optional storage| Database[PostgreSQL /<br/>MariaDB /<br/>MySQL]

    %% Internal RHOAI Dependencies
    TrustyAI -->|payload injection| KServe[KServe]
    TrustyAI -->|payload injection| ModelMesh[ModelMesh Serving]
    TrustyAI -.->|dashboard integration| Dashboard[ODH / RHOAI Dashboard<br/>Optional]

    %% Integration Points
    KServe -->|inference payloads| TrustyAI
    ModelMesh -->|payload data| TrustyAI
    Prometheus[Prometheus] -->|scrapes metrics| TrustyAI
    OAuth[OpenShift OAuth] -->|token validation| TrustyAI
    Routes[OpenShift Routes] -->|external exposure| TrustyAI

    %% API Server Interaction
    K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server] <-->|reconciliation| TrustyAI

